The paper discusses a neural network model that can learn algorithms and generalize to inputs of arbitrary length, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is based on a specific architecture called the Neural GPU, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
